<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>LazyDeclutter | End Clutter Paralysis in 15 Minutes</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
       .hero-gradient { background: linear-gradient(180deg, #F5F5F0 0%, #FFFFFF 100%); }
       .accent-orange { color: #E67E22; }
       .bg-accent-orange { background-color: #E67E22; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-white text-gray-900">

    <section class="hero-gradient pt-20 pb-12 px-6 text-center">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black tracking-tight mb-6">
                End <span class="accent-orange">Clutter Paralysis</span> <br>in 15 Minutes.
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-600 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                Meet Dusty, the witty AI Sloth who acts as your judge. Point your camera, get a verdict, and reclaim your home.
            </p>
            
            <div class="max-w-md mx-auto mb-12">
                <form action="https://formspree.io/f/mykwajpr" method="POST" class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4">
                    <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Enter your email" required 
                        class="flex-1 px-6 py-4 rounded-2xl border-2 border-gray-200 focus:border-orange-500 outline-none text-lg">
                    <button type="submit" class="bg-accent-orange text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-2xl font-bold text-lg hover:opacity-90 transition-all shadow-lg">
                        Get Early Access
                    </button>
                </form>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-4 italic">Join 500+ early testers. No login required for daily habits.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="relative max-w-sm mx-auto shadow-2xl rounded-[3rem] border-[12px] border-gray-900 overflow-hidden">
                <img src="dusty.glass.light.png" alt="LazyDeclutter App Interface" class="w-full">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 px-6 bg-gray-50 text-center">
        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto grid md:grid-grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            <div class="text-left">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-4 uppercase tracking-wider text-gray-400">The "Expert" Judge</h2>
                <h3 class="text-4xl font-black mb-6 italic">"Dusty doesn't care about your feelings."</h3>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6">
                    Stuck on an item? Ask Dusty. He uses "Time vs. Money" logic to identify your stuff and issue a command: 
                    <span class="font-bold">SELL, DONATE, or TOSS.</span>
                </p>
                <ul class="space-y-4 text-left">
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-lg font-bold">
                        <span class="bg-green-100 p-2 rounded-full text-green-600">✓</span> 
                        Real-time Resale Valuations (Image 2/6)
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-lg font-bold">
                        <span class="bg-green-100 p-2 rounded-full text-green-600">✓</span> 
                        Privacy-First On-Device AI
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-center">
                <img src="dusty.glass.light.mode.png" alt="Dusty the Sloth Scanning" class="w-72 md:w-96 drop-shadow-xl">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 px-6 text-center">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <div class="inline-block bg-orange-100 text-orange-600 px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-bold tracking-widest mb-4">
                THE 15-MINUTE HABIT
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-8 leading-tight">
                One Micro-Mission a Day.<br>A Lifetime of Serenity.
            </h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-12">
                We're restoring the vanished "Toss" app loop. Bite-sized daily challenges focused strictly on item removal. 
                Track your progress with our <span class="accent-orange font-bold">Dopamine Tally</span>.
            </p>
           
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
                <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                    <img src="dusty.stuff.light.mode.png" alt="Toss it" class="w-20 mx-auto mb-4">
                    <h4 class="font-black">TOSS IT</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                    <img src="dusty.sold.light.mode.png" alt="Sell it" class="w-20 mx-auto mb-4">
                    <h4 class="font-black uppercase tracking-tight">CASH IN</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                    <img src="dusty.hang.light.mode.png" alt="Success" class="w-20 mx-auto mb-4">
                    <h4 class="font-black uppercase tracking-tight">DONE</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="p-6 bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100">
                    <img src="dusty.yeh.light.mode.png" alt="YEH! YEH!" class="w-20 mx-auto mb-4">
                    <h4 class="font-black uppercase tracking-tight">DOPAMINE HIT</h4>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="bg-gray-900 text-white py-20 px-6 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-black mb-6 italic">Ready to make progress?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto">
            LazyDeclutter is launching soon. Join the waitlist now to receive a <span class="text-white font-bold italic">Lifetime Premium Pass</span> if you are one of the first 500 signups.
        </p>
        <a href="#" class="inline-block bg-accent-orange px-10 py-5 rounded-2xl font-black text-xl hover:scale-105 transition-all shadow-xl uppercase tracking-widest">
            Lock In My Spot
        </a>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
